author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session and interview of Charlie Parr featuring previously unreleased footage, from when he visited The Current studio back in 2015.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Over the Cedar
00:04:12 Interview Pt 1
00:11:38 Frank Miller Blues
00:15:44 Interview Pt 2
00:24:10 Falcon

Musicians
Charlie Parr — vocals, guitar

Credits
Host — David Campbell
Producer – David Campbell
Engineer – Michael DeMark
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
